Title: 127: No Compromise: Tableau, Twitter and Fearless Career Shifts
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the Head of Business Intelligence at EXASOL, Eva Murray. You will listen to the start of a visual analytics journey, hear about Eva's career decisions which took her around the world, learn about Tableau and an intro to those who are new to the tool, and learn about the current opportunities at Exasol.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/127
